&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;f41(&amp;amp;a, &amp;amp;b, &amp;amp;c);&lt;/code&gt;  – 此時 a = 5, b = 3, c = 1。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;f41(int* p, int* q, int* r)&lt;/code&gt;  – 此時 p = &amp;amp;a, q = &amp;amp;b, r = &amp;amp;c。&lt;/li&gt;
